<br>
 <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Maybe all the stores were like closed or something and they didn't want me to accidently go shopping while no one was there. These big foreheady peoples here seem kinda grumpy like that, not like Sergy's friends</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> she thought. Seeing the priestess, wearing in Tanare's opinion a cute balck outfit though something definitely needed to be done about her hair, tapping her foot impatiently she decided to get down to business.<br>
<br>
  &quot;Dear Meledy singy-person,<br>
<br>
  &quot;I know like mother wanted you to like keep track of me and stuff so the big foreheady person named Littany told me to be sure to write you and like let you know where i am. I was killing the bad doggies with Dronky and he told me there was a special sale in that paineel city place. Did you know there was ANOTHER big foreheady person city around cause i didn;t i just thought like Sergy's city was the only one?<br>
<br>
  &quot;Anyways, they had some cute fountains and stuff, and all the big foreheady people were nice like Dronky cause they like rescued those poor skele people stuck outside doing that mining stuff with like no pay or days off. They looked at me funny though and seemed a little grumpy though.<br>
<br>
   &quot;So we looked around and stuff and finally he took me inside this building and all where we saw the Littany big foreheady person there, cause she must have been like in charge of the dress shop there. Anyways we talked and it seemed like Littany and Dronky knew each other or something, i think they both knew this Lord Thuley guy or something.<br>
<br>
   &quot;So i was asking about the outfit when they asked me to like put my weapons away, probably so i wouldn;t accidently cut the dresses or nothing there even though i didn;t see any but maybe they are all in another room. Then Dronky put these wristbands on with this big chain on them, they didn't really match my outfit but i figured it was like a free sample or something for a new customer. Then the Littany person hung the other end of the chain on the wall for some reason, maybe so i wouldn't like trip over it or nothing, cause if i tripped and like bumped my head or something i might sue them or something. These big foreheady peoples are pretty wierd sometimes.<br>
<br>
   &quot;Anyways, after this, Littany person asked me to write to you cause she didn;t want you to be worried or nothin about where i was. She told me there were even going to have a party for me so i guess maybe they didn't want me to stumble into where they were setting the party up or nothing cause she must know i like parties and presents and stuff. Oooh yeah, she also told me she was even going to have a special dress made up just for me! isn't that nice? maybe tomorrow they'll take me to some of the shops so i can let them know what material i like bestest.<br>
<br>
   &quot;I know Sergy is really behind this cause all the peoples in his city must have told them how warm and fuzzy they felt about me when i went to visit there this morning. He was just like pretending to not like me and stuff cause that would like break some big foreheady person rule or something.<br>
<br>
   &quot;So anyways, the bigforeheady person is like tapping her foot so i guess she wants me to like finish or something, i don';t know why since she was the one who wanted me to write this in the first place but i think she's kinda grumpy or something. Do you beleive she actually asked me if i knew how to write? Does she think i'm like stupid or something?<br>
<br>
   &quot;Ok her eyes are starting to get all big and bulgy now so i guess i'll like finish now. So when i get back i'll be sure to show you all the nice stuff i'll buy here... oh wait you WILL be at the party right? Ok have to go now for real like.<br>
<br>
   &quot;Signed<br>
    Tanare<br>
    adorably cute<br>
    League of Honory person<br>
    did i mention i'm cute?&quot;<br>
<br>
  <br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Finally!</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> Littany thought to herself as the wood elf finished the letter and handed it to her. Skimming it quickly Littany rolled her eyes wondering how the wood elves could continue as a race with such as this among them. Sealing it , she addressed the note to Meledi Weaver, League of Honour halls.Calling a minion she handed it the letter and said.<br>
<br>
  &quot;Take this to the bard netwrok, they will be sure to deliver it to the proper place.&quot;<br>
<br>
   Looking back at the captive, who was staring back at her with visions of dresses dancing in her eyes, Thule's priestess said. &quot;Very good child, now if you'll excuse me I have other matters to attend to. Someone will be by later to feed you if you are hungry.&quot; and strode from the room ignoring the wood elf who waved goodbye to her and asked if she could  have a salad with little pieces of cheese mixed in and a brownie for dessert when it came time for supper because her mother always gave her brownies when she was good.<br>
<br>
