<br>
   <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Boy these dressy maker peoples must not get a lot of business or nothin if that have to like chain peoples to the walls to make sure they don;t leave and go to another shop or nothing.</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> she thought to herself as she waited. She missed the outdoors already and the fact that all the &quot;bad doggie healy peoples&quot; were no doubt repopulating the Warrens as she waited. <br>
<br>
  <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Well maybe Dronky is taking care of them. it was very rude of him not to tell me when he was coming back though, snobby pally guy</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> she decided still a bit annoyed that dronkarr had turned and left without her. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>I mean we DO have other shops to visit once i get my dress here and all</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
  Hearing footsteps outside the room she called out  &quot;Hey bigforeheady person is there some place i can like get some food or something?&quot; before she stopped as the door openned and a robed figure walked inside.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>This is surely an honor the priestess has bestowed upon me </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> thought the novice at the honor of being put in charge of feeding the sacrifice before the cerimony. The almost amused look on Littany's face when she gave him the task seemed odd, but he thought perhaps it was a sign of being pleased with his work.<br>
<br>
    He was startled out of his thoughts when a chipper sounding voice asked  him, &quot;ooh is that mine? I don't see any brownies there, i told the dressy maker person that i wanted brownies!&quot; Tanare declared as she saw the bread cheese and water the novice brought to her. <br>
<br>
    Rising to her feet Tanare stomped her foot on the ground and demanded, &quot;I SAID i wanted a SALAD with the cheese not bread! I mean you big foreheady peoples must have like two brains up there or something and you can't even get my dinner right?&quot; she said poutingly.<br>
<br>
   Looking down his nose at her the novice said, &quot;This is what I have been told to give to you, eat or do not eat, Lord Thule will be satisfied regardless.&quot; and put the tray of food on the table.<br>
<br>
   &quot;ooh Lord THULE is coming to my party yippee?&quot; Tanare clapped happily, before she paused and asked with a confused look in her eyes, &quot;Who's Lord Thule?&quot;<br>
<br>
   At that the novice's eyes nearly bulged out of his head. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Who is LORD THULE! What sort of ignorant fool is this elf?</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
A faint sinister smile on his face the novice replied, &quot;Lord Thule is our Lord and master, you will become acquainted with his ways soon enough so you will be ready when it is time for your...'party' &quot;<br>
<br>
  He watched the elf think about it some before she answered  &quot;OK..um what's aquainted mean?&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Now i understand the smile</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> the novice thought as he thought back to the priestess when she gave him this assignment. Addressing the elf again he replied, &quot;Nevermind it is not important.&quot; and watched her smile again as if a great weight had been lifted from her shoulders.<br>
<br>
  &quot;So anyways,&quot; Tanare began again, &quot; next time i want like a nice bowl of yummy rabbit stew, ooh muffins, yes blueberry muffins are always good and some fruit juice to drink too.&quot; nodding to herself she added &quot;oh and when will the dressmakers come by to measure me so they make sure the dress is in my size and all, extra elfin petite but you need like exact measurements so it doesn't like hang off me like a coat or something uncute like that. Do you think they will be a long time? Cause the bad doggies are coming back and i have to kill them all some more before they're like everywhere and stuff.&quot; <br>
<br>
   Then gazing more carefully at the novice she added &quot;and you know those robes don't really go well with your skin tone, and you really need to let your hair grow out some more cause it likes make you look like you have a bigger forehead than a regular big foreheady person does and you might like spin around some day and then fall over cause your forehead was like too big and all and tipped you over.&quot;<br>
<br>
   &quot;Oh yeah and like when i can go take a bath cause if i'm going to be here a while to get my dress done right i'll get like all icky and stuff and my hair will get all dirty and greasy if i don't wash it 4 times a day. and we can't let that happen. So if you see the littany person could you like ask her this for me and stuff cause i can't even sharpen my weapons or nothing cuase they're like way over on the other side of the room and stuff when she put them there by mistake even though i promised her i wouldn't like take them out and mess up the dresses or nothing but she wouldn't listen...&quot;<br>
<br>
