Dearest Flamerge,<br>
<br>
Well, I should say that an affront has been perpetrated, one both scandalous and meretricious!  I have found myself so positively and uncharacteristically nettled.  Perhaps you have heard such rumors and insinuations?  I know not, but I must set to record the events leading to my current state.  As to  the perpetrator...I suspect you already know the name, as this one has been a veritable thorn in my side for some time now.  And so, I shall preface this revelation to provide the proper context, so that you may understand my distress.<br>
